  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Gift of Vision and Hearing to Children</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Across Africa, children are facing discrimination due to hearing and vision difficulties. With families lacking knowledge of identifying problems, and resources to provide adequate support, many children fall behind in school. This results in lack of employment opportunities and coping strategies causing dependency on families, governments and international aid. By providing children with the gift of vision and hearing, they can grow and develop and become part of the solution.</narrative>
  </description>
